None structural. Two notes outside my remit (cohesion only), already tracked in the draft's own ledgers: the final section's opening sentence ("The numbers around John Goodman finally moving in the right direction tell a late story") reads a little awkwardly as written — a word-choice fix for the line editor, not a cohesion issue. And `faqs` frontmatter is still pending the enrich stage. The through-line itself is clean end to end.
